sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant ChangesApp as Changes Webview
participant ChangesRouter as ChangesMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as ChangesUseCases
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime
participant Vscode as VscodeGitRuntime

User->>ChangesApp: Open Changes view
ChangesApp->>ChangesRouter: changes/statusRequest(repositoryLocator, worktreeLocator, requestId)
ChangesRouter->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>ChangesRouter: Worktree
ChangesRouter->>UseCase: getStatus(Worktree, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: getStatus(signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: GitStatus
Runtime-->>Worktree: GitStatus
Worktree-->>UseCase: GitStatus
UseCase-->>ChangesRouter: GitStatus
ChangesRouter-->>ChangesApp: changes/statusResponse(requestId, status)
ChangesApp-->>User: Render staged, unstaged, conflicts, stash, submodules

User->>ChangesApp: Commit staged changes
ChangesApp->>ChangesRouter: changes/commit(worktreeLocator, message, requestId)
ChangesRouter->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>ChangesRouter: Worktree
ChangesRouter->>UseCase: commit(Worktree, message, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: commit(message, signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: commit(executionContext, message, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: commit(executionContext, message, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: success
Runtime-->>Worktree: success
Worktree-->>UseCase: success
UseCase-->>ChangesRouter: success
ChangesRouter-->>ChangesApp: changes/commitResponse(requestId)
ChangesRouter-->>ChangesApp: changes/refreshRequested

alt Follow-up remote sync requested
  ChangesApp->>ChangesRouter: changes/push(worktreeLocator, remote, requestId)
  ChangesRouter->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
  Registry-->>ChangesRouter: Worktree
  ChangesRouter->>UseCase: push(Worktree, remote, signal)
  UseCase->>Worktree: push(remote, signal)
  Worktree->>Runtime: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
  alt VS Code runtime can provide credentials
    Runtime->>Vscode: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
    Vscode-->>Runtime: success
  else CLI credentials are available
    Runtime->>Cli: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
    Cli-->>Runtime: success
  end
  Runtime-->>Worktree: success
  Worktree-->>UseCase: success
  UseCase-->>ChangesRouter: success
  ChangesRouter-->>ChangesApp: changes/pushResponse(requestId)
  ChangesRouter-->>ChangesApp: changes/refreshRequested
end
